						"title": "Beyond the checklist",
						"subtitle": "Modernizing compliance in an AI-driven world",
						"copy": "GenAI brings the same game-changing economies of scale to cyberattackers as it does\nto enterprises, only attackers don't abide by the rules. As usage evolves, organizations face new risks, additional regulations, and expanded requirements to demonstrate both threat prevention capabilities and regulatory compliance. Regulators and individual countries continue to move fast but CISOs can't afford to wait for laws to expand their compliance programs. CISOs must find ways to bolster existing defenses against AI-led attacks and prevent LLMs from becoming new vectors for inbound and outbound threats.\n\nLearn how to think beyond compliance checkboxes. Address the following challenges GenAI brings to your organization:\n- Keeping up with new regulations as their threat landscape evolves\n- Balancing risk, productivity, and adherence\n- Managing the AI compliance journey\n\n![Data Anywhere Thumbnail](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/2lq5tWk1LSTJKdHNVSeGsG/a7c70ce8481618141f0d3603b9d143b6/Data_Anywhere_Thumbnail.png)",
